ygData.messageBody:
Humm I guess I got extremly lucky then cause at 40 I soloed her once... I
was killing her with my friend a 50 wiz's help, and he went linkdead right
as she popped... i was expecting to die, but tried to fight anyways. Was a
REALLY close fight, but I ended up winning. Although she did fear me once,
and if the caves had had any spawns in them I would have died to the
specs...
